---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Card from "../components/Card.astro";
import "./styles/global.css";
---

<Layout title="欢迎来到Astro">
    <main>
        <nav>
            <a href="/">首页</a>
            <a href="/about/">关于</a>
            <a href="/blog/">博客</a>
            <a href="/notes/">笔记</a>
        </nav>
        <h1 class="text-gradient">课程笔记</h1>
        <p>在这个页面，我将展示一些关于我的课程笔记。</p>
    </main>
    <section class="link-card-grid">
      <article class="link-card">
        <a href="/md/1" >陋室铭赏析</a>
      <article class="link-card">
            <a href="/md/2" >Astro 安装及部署</a>
        </article>
        <article class="link-card">
            <a href="/md/3" >在Astro中创建页面及链接</a>
            <article class="link-card">
        </article>
    </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    margin: auto;
    padding: 1rem;
    width: 800px;
    max-width: calc(100% - 2rem);
    color: rgb(245, 222, 226);
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  nav a {
    color: rgb(245, 222, 226);
    text-decoration: none;
    margin: 0 10px;
  }
  
  .astro-a {
    display: block;
    margin: 5px 0; /* 调整间距 */
  }
  
  h1.text-gradient {
    /* ... */
  }
  
  @keyframes gradient-animation {
    /* ... */
  }
  
  .link-card-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 2rem;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  
  .link-card {
    flex-basis: calc(50% - 2rem); /* 两列布局，减去间距 */
    box-sizing: border-box;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  /* 响应式调整 */
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .link-card {
      flex-basis: 100%; /* 在小屏幕上占满整行 */
    }
  }
</style>
